import express from "express"
import { handleHome } from "../controllers/userController"

const globalRouter = express.Router()
globalRouter.get('/', handleHome)

export default globalRouter

import express from "express"
import { handleEdit } from "../controllers/userController"


const userRouter = express.Router()
userRouter.get("/edit", handleEdit)

export default userRouter

import express from "express"
import { handleWatch, handleRemove } from "../controllers/videoController"


const videoRouter = express.Router()
videoRouter.get('/watch', handleWatch)
videoRouter.get('/remove', handleRemove)

export default videoRouter

export const handleHome = (req, res) => res.send("Home sweet home")
export const handleEdit = (req, res) => res.send("Edit users")

export const handleWatch = (req, res) => res.send("Watch videos")
export const handleRemove = (req, res) => res.send("Remove videos")
